1. 1) Make it conscious; 2) Make it a game; 3) Make it competitive; 4) Make it small and temporary

2. Measurement = Motivation. Seeing progress in changing numbers makes the repetitive fascinating and creates a positive feedback loop.

3. MAC OS: ctrl + cmd + F = Full Screen. Amazingly focusing on what you're doing!

4. Youtube: captions->options->Background- opacity -> 25%


